Samsung is now defending a patent infringement suit in the Eastern District of Texas, filed by Estech Systems IP, LLC and assigned to Judge Gilstrap. That venue and that judge mean one thing above all else: the clock starts fast. Gilstrap's docket moves on its own schedule, and NPE plaintiffs filing there know exactly how to use that pressure.

Stilta runs rapid prior-art and invalidity searches against the asserted patents, builds claim charts, and helps in-house teams frame an IPR or PTAB strategy before the case sets its own pace. We work specifically on patent litigation support, so we can be useful within days, not weeks.

If it would help, we can put together a short overview of how we would approach the asserted patents in Estech Systems IP, LLC v. Samsung Electronics Co., Ltd. and share it with your team this week. Happy to set up a brief call if that is easier.

